Revision history for Perl distribution Dist-Zilla-Deb

0.04 2013-09-07
    - Reformatted Changes file as per CPAN::Changes::Spec
      (thanks to github:neilbowers, PR #4)

0.03 2011-10-28
    - prune tfiles dir from distribution and prevent xt/packages from indexing.
      RT#71998.

0.02 2010-11-12
    - debuild command propagates some options (mostly for the tests)
    - Deb::VersionFromChangelog plugin implemented

0.01 2010-11-11
    - Initial release
    - 'debuild', 'debc', 'debi' and 'debrelease' commands implemented.

